metadata.name: Witch Of The Forest
metadata.description: Beware! Wanderers of the woods. Bards and knights and brave adventurers. You are drawn to this dark forest. The forest might be a shortcut, might have a treasure or might contain your desires. One thing is sure, The Witch of the forest is here. Her flame like hair and beautiful face will give you comfort and warmt. But her bony fingers and fiery eyes will take your soul. This is her hunting ground. This is her dining table. Once the nocturnal night begins, you will hear the wind whispering and trees rustling. You will hear a calm and inviting voice singing. Take the invitation, step into the shadows. And you will see her eyes burning.
